院已经没有病床了。纽约地铁最近几天则面临数千名员工缺勤的状况，相关服务都因此受到影响，纽约消防局缺勤的消防员更是达平常的 2 倍之多。此外，洛杉矶目前已有近千名警察和消防员因确诊新冠被隔离，导致出警缓慢。而亚利桑那州的凤凰城天港国际机场则是没有足够的运输安全管理局人员到岗，使得机场最繁忙的两处安检站不得不关闭。美国累计新冠肺炎确诊病例超 6000 万例"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-30c5cdb20e5b1f9ca3bd05f4ac033d5f_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "280 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/510740158"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iq9Ol4NjOqOlfEAMaCDc1Nzc5NDE1IOSP7o4GMBc4hQJACXIJNTEwNzQwMTU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1641870468.2694707", "card_id": "Q_510755371", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 43}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么《雪中悍刀行》大家都不想飞升仙界，为什么把仙界描述的那么可怕？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-295cdacb2508e736b0e0634da63b3f3d_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "266 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/510755371"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iq9Ol4NjOqOlfEAMaCDc1NzgyODIzINat7o4GMAY4UkAKcgk1MTA3NTUzNzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1641870468.2698288", "card_id": "Q_508534148", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 140}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我去峨眉山旅游峨眉山的猴子攻击我我一个左勾拳给猴子打晕了，算伤害野生动物吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-ac2f7ad70bfb63450642de7e25a865e4_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "252 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/508534148"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iq9Ol4NjOqOlfEAMaCDc1Mjg5MTg2ILLhpI4GMB84mQJAC3IJNTA4NTM0MTQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1641870468.2702417", "card_id": "Q_51005822